Regression: FAIL_013 — on a 3-node RF=1 sharded table, the public wrapper
emitted on every node must include agents for the shards that live on
the OTHER two nodes. Old behaviour filtered against the master's nodeId
in every wrapper, dropping the master's shard from non-master nodes.

